    <h1 style="margin-top:16px;">How Much Compensation Can I Get for Workplace Discrimination?</h1>
    <p>Workplace discrimination victims may be entitled to back pay, front pay, emotional distress damages, punitive damages, and attorney's fees. The total value depends heavily on which law applies, the severity of the conduct, and your state's rules.</p>
    <div class="meta">
      <div class="meta-item">📅 Last Reviewed: June 2026</div>
      <div class="meta-item">✍ Reviewed By: <a href="author-bios.html" style="color:var(--sky-deep);text-decoration:underline;">Michael E. Vance, Esq.</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container" style="padding-top:32px;">
